{
  "stem": "25114.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And desks, usually two in a desk.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You just sit.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And my teacher-- our teacher even made us in the middle of the lesson go out of the desk and make some exercises so we wouldn't have anything bent, you know, bad backs.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Stretch so we had good posture.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So she made us even every half hour go out of the-- and make some exercises.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they cared about us so much.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I didn't change schools.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because when I came out of school, I was, what, 14 and a half.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was-- I don't want to brag, but I was top-- top [INAUDIBLE] top of my classes [INAUDIBLE] in my schooling.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I was very wrapped up.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I just-- so thirsty, really, absolutely literally thirsting for knowledge.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And my teacher called me, and she said, I'll put you in for a scholarship.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the education was private.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We couldn't get into secondary education.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was more than-- lighter than secondarily.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I mean, this school was sort of like today, used to be here intermediate, or something like. that.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But I took-- I got my education different-- in a different way.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I went to-- we had very active groups of people which were students or already qualified teachers or doctors, and they took us-- those very intelligent kids.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so my dad organized us into self-education, and everybody gets their time freely.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so I studied biology, and psychology, and literature, and history.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I've read, and I've read, and I've read.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I've read libraries.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I was just very, very keen.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Being in Warsaw, we were exposed to a lot of culture, Yiddish, and Polish, and international, you know.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I was a music lover, so I really educated myself in this time.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
